p.span: The mission of the Millville Public Charter School is to provide a nurturing, supportive, creative and actively engaging environment for students and families that facilitates the performing and visual arts and development of well-educated and responsible young adults with a life long love of learning.

p.span:
Registration Process
Applying to attend the Millville Public Charter School
To enter your child into the selection lottery for admission to the Millville Public Charter School, you will need to fill out a Student Application.

span.span: Upon completion of the Application, please send it to

p.span:
If you prefer, you may fax the completed application to:
856-506-8143
Welcome to Millville Public Charter School, A public K-8 school where hard work and happiness equal success! Go ahead and click around, there is a ton of new stuff to check out.
